The Holy War is over
The demons of Gologotha have been banished, yet the cost has been terribly high
The Creator, god of the Fyllid, has been defeated and the faith of the people has begun to wane
Petty squabbles among the five remaining gods has caused the land to split into five mystical territories - each at war with one another
Into this divided land steps a wizard, a man haunted by his past, whose choices will shape the future.